name: Kan'u Unchou (Ikkitousen)
description:
Lora model of Kan'u Unchou from Ikkitousen. Preview images done with weight 1.

This one is simple because it only has one outfit, but I still put an effort to make it work well. I had problem with hair and depending on prompt you may have to add low-tied long hair, hair over one eye to the prompt. Still depending on image model can struggle with hair shape making sense when it's not fully visible.

Other than that earring didn't really came out accurate, even after I retrained with just that in mind >_<

Full outfit prompt - kanu unchou, fingerless gloves, serafuku, midriff, loose socks, pleated skirt, yellow neckerchief, earrings, loafers

Additionally tags torn clothes, torn shirt, torn skirt, underboob work well.
